---
// CoDesign.astro
---
<section id="values" class="values" aria-labelledby="values-heading">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 id="values-heading" class="sr-only">Values</h2>
    <ul class="values__grid" role="list">
      <li>
        <article class="value-card">
          <img src="/assets/values-autonomy.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>Autonomy</h3>
          <p>Supporting independent communication.</p>
          <a href="#autonomy-overlay">Autonomy details</a>
        </article>
      </li>
      <li>
        <article class="value-card">
          <img src="/assets/values-accessibility.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>Accessibility</h3>
          <p>Designed with sensory, motor, and attentional needs in mind.</p>
          <a href="#accessibility-overlay">Accessibility commitments</a>
        </article>
      </li>
      <li>
        <article class="value-card">
          <img src="/assets/values-codesign.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>Co-Design</h3>
          <p>Built together with nonspeaking autistic collaborators.</p>
          <a href="#codesign-overlay">How co-design works</a>
        </article>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="values__cta">
      <a href="#process" class="btn">Explore</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="process" class="process" aria-labelledby="process-heading">
  <div class="process__inner section-inner">
    <div class="process__left">
      <h2 id="process-heading">Process with a purpose</h2>
      <img src="/assets/process-illustration.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="process__right">
      <article>
        <h3>Co-design, not top-down</h3>
        <p>
          TYPE is developed with nonspeaking autistic people, not for them. Their lived experiences
          guide priorities, ensure relevance, and shape outcomes.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Iterative &amp; adaptive</h3>
        <p>
          We test, listen, and revise continuously. This process allows TYPE to support diverse
          communication needs across contexts.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Transparency &amp; trust</h3>
        <p>
          We share progress and challenges openly. By working together and sharing decisions, we build
          trust within our team and with the wider community.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div id="autonomy-overlay" class="overlay" aria-label="Autonomy in practice">
  <div class="overlay__card">
    <h3 class="overlay__title">Autonomy in practice</h3>
    <div class="overlay__body">
      <p>Examples include adjustable predictions, user-controlled prompts, and transparent feedback.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="overlay__actions">
      <a href="#journey" class="btn">Get Updates</a>
    </div>
    <a href="#values" class="overlay__close">Close</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="accessibility-overlay" class="overlay" aria-label="Accessibility commitments">
  <div class="overlay__card">
    <h3 class="overlay__title">Accessibility commitments</h3>
    <div class="overlay__body">
      <p>
        TYPE includes sensory-aware contrast, flexible interaction pacing, and motor-supportive layout
        choices co-reviewed with collaborators.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="overlay__actions">
      <a href="#journey" class="btn">Get Updates</a>
    </div>
    <a href="#values" class="overlay__close">Close</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="codesign-overlay" class="overlay" aria-label="How co-design works">
  <div class="overlay__card">
    <h3 class="overlay__title">How co-design works</h3>
    <div class="overlay__body">
      <p>
        Nonspeaking autistic collaborators, supporters, and researchers shape goals, review prototypes,
        and inform decisions through each project cycle.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="overlay__actions">
      <a href="#journey" class="btn">Get Updates</a>
    </div>
    <a href="#values" class="overlay__close">Close</a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .values {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding-block: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .values__grid {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(13.75rem, 1fr));
  }

  .value-card {
    text-align: center;
    border: 0.0625rem solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 1.2rem;
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }

  .value-card img {
    width: 5.125rem;
    height: 5.125rem;
    object-fit: contain;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .value-card a {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .values__cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .process {
    background: var(--color-surface-alt);
    color: #111;
    padding-block: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .process__inner {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }

  .process__left h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5.4vw, 3.6rem);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .process__left img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 22.5rem;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .process__right article {
    padding-block: 0.8rem;
    border-bottom: 0.0625rem solid #6d6d6d;
  }

  .process__right h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .process__right p {
    color: #2b2b2b;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 50em) {
    .process__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
